title: Top 10 WORST Movies 2021
description: More of a "Top 10 Disappointing Movies" list, but as Hollywood will never stop churning out disappointing garbage in the name of making a buck, I figure I might as well rank the ones I saw in 2021.

title: Top 10 BEST Movies 2021
description: Another year comes to an end, and while I didn't see as many movies this year as I usually do, I do have 10 that I liked most. So here is the list of my TOP 10 FAVORITE MOVIES OF 2021!
